\par }\pard \ql \fi720\li0\ri0\sl480\slmult1\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {Of course, this all rehearses a rather old feminist critique of the phallogocentric discourse of \'93whole/part\'94
